title: BEAUTIFUL SPACIOUS 2 bed, 2 bath FAMILY TOWNHOME
posting_body: ['Large, newer 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom townhome.', 'Built in 2002.', '1120', 'sq ft.', 'Well laid out, spacious and airy.', 'Not back-to-back with another house.', 'Open in front and back.', 'Split level has short flight up to the living room, dining room, kitchen.', 'Very tall ceilings.', 'Large windows for natural light.', 'Dining room has a walk-out deck facing east so shaded in the afternoon.', 'Both bedrooms and the two bathrooms are up a short stairway.', 'Master bedroom is huge with a walk-in closet and a bathroom.', 'Newer carpet throughout.', 'Very open concept and neutral wall colors.', 'Large attached 2-car garage.', 'Close to shopping, on a bus line, and near major roads.', 'Quiet neighborhood and well maintained by the association.', 'We pay their monthly fee, which includes trash, lawn care, and snow removal.', 'Sorry, no smoking and no pets.', 'We do not participate in voucher programs.', 'Available 1 Sept.']
